PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by the PROVINCE OF SASKATCHEWAN of its statutory power to acquire two parcels of land (45.649 hectares in all) situated within Opaskwayak Cree Nation Indian Reserve No. 27A, for highway and public utility purposes, and (b) transferring the land in question to the province for those purposes, in lieu thereof.
